<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 18:10:56 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>内塔尼亚胡部长希望任命针对他的案件的证人担任主要职务</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-minister-looking-to-appoint-witness-in-case-against-him-to-major-position/00000191-7aff-d8d0-a7bb-fbffd4150000</link><description>以色列能源部长、前外交部长伊莱·科恩因出于政治原因向不符合资格的人士发放外交护照而受到调查。他希望任命该案主要警方证人罗南·莱维（Ronen Levi）担任以色列国家能源基础设施公司的负责人</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 17:43:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-minister-looking-to-appoint-witness-in-case-against-him-to-major-position/00000191-7aff-d8d0-a7bb-fbffd4150000</guid></item><item><title>以色列处于战争状态，第 321 天：摩萨德和辛贝特酋长抵达开罗，在峰会前进行会谈</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-321-mossad-shin-bet-chiefs-land-in-cairo-for-talks-ahead-of-summit/00000191-7af5-dacb-afb3-fbffae730001</link><description>据报道，内塔尼亚胡在与拜登通话时表示愿意在与哈马斯的停火谈判中妥协 ■ 以色列国防军表示，本周早些时候从加沙打捞上来的六名人质尸体上发现了枪声 ■ 以色列国防军首席检察官指控五名预备役军人严重虐待哈马斯警察Sde Teiman 拘留中心的官员 ■ 战争进入 321 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 16:45:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-321-mossad-shin-bet-chiefs-land-in-cairo-for-talks-ahead-of-summit/00000191-7af5-dacb-afb3-fbffae730001</guid></item><item><title>黎巴嫩努力解决陷入瘫痪的电力供应危机</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/lebanon-struggles-to-solve-power-supply-crisis-paralyzing-the-country/00000191-7abe-de08-a3f9-7bbfc6d90000</link><description>黎巴嫩最后一座大型发电厂被迫关闭后，该国已经笼罩在黑暗之中一个多星期了。政府正在努力确保燃料捐赠（主要来自阿尔及利亚），以提供部分解决方案</descript